      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a benchmark for front-midship balance, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with its sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger system. The powerplant delivers linear boost across the rev range, managed by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry utilizes aluminum double-wishbones at all four corners, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. This example maintains its factory aerodynamics and lightweight ethos, with a cooling system upgrade to ensure thermal efficiency under load. A purist\u2019s driving machine with crisp throttle response and a rigid, lightweight frame ready for the canyon or the track.",
